data.description: Very cute ranch style home only 7 mins. from downtown Knoxville.  Less than 10 to UT campus.  Original 1950's hardwood floors flow through most of the home with luxury vinyl tile in the kitchen and bathroom.  Stainless appliances, white cabinets and butcher block counter tops.  Very cool retro vibe.  Call today to get your showing scheduled.
